## Decision Trees

### [Common Decision Type]

```
Is [condition A]?
├── Yes → [Action/Framework to use]
└── No
    ├── Is [condition B]?
    │   ├── Yes → [Action]
    │   └── No → [Action]
    └── Default → [Fallback action]
```

